::Prowl::

Prowl looks back at Iron Raptor as she looks at him and growls, for a 
second thinking that she was growling at him. He holds her up as she 
leans up against him, looking back at Iris.

"Almost," he says, checking his spark signature. 603.51165, 
603.51169, 603.51173, 603.5117!

"Ready!" Prowl says, his spark stabalizing at 603.5117, "Now what do 
we have to do?"





--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
> 
> 
> * Iron Raptor simply looks over the field one more time before 
looking at

modes

both of you 
> will come out repaired in the end."

looking back

> But at the mention at her injuries she was, once again, reminded of 
her 
> wounded shoulder, shifting her weight to keep off of it.
> Iron Raptor turned her head in surprise towards Prowl as he layed a 
> concerned hand on her shoulder, seeing his equally sight of concern 
as well
> 
> She sighed and leaned against him a bit, but not too much because 
she might 
> push him over.
> She was tired, sore, in pain and just sick of everything. She just 
wanted 
> this over and done with so that she could get back to the CF and 
being 
> commander of the Maximals.*
> 
> IRIS: " Prowl, if you're ready maybe we could start?"
